

REQUIREMENTS

The following equipment have been employed:

1. Linux Mint 17.3 Rosa

2. Zybo board

3. Vivado v2015.4 (64 bits)




STEPS

1. Download the u-boot Repository for Digilent FPGA Boards from GitHub:

#COPY FROM HERE:
wget 'https://github.com/Digilent/u-boot-Digilent-Dev/archive/master-next.zip' -O u-boot-Digilent-Dev-master-next.zip
unzip u-boot-Digilent-Dev-master-next.zip -d unzip_folder	
cd unzip_folder/
mv u-boot-Digilent-Dev-master-next/ ../
cd ..
rm -rf unzip_folder/
rm u-boot-Digilent-Dev-master-next.zip

#TO HERE



2. Set necessary variables on the bash shell

export ARCH=arm
export CROSS_COMPILE=arm-xilinx-linux-gnueabi-
source /opt/Xilinx/Vivado/2015.4/settings64.sh 
export echo PATH=$PWD/u-boot-Digilent-Dev-master-next/tools:$PATH



3. 









